# Site core

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) at session start for repo map, content rules, and backlog.

## Stack

Astro 6 static site, pnpm, Tailwind. Deploy: push to **`master`** → GitHub Pages → `rafaelroman.com`.

## Before finishing UI work

1. Run affected page in browser (`pnpm dev`, localhost:4321)
2. Check light **and** dark theme if colors/layout changed
3. Run `pnpm build && pnpm lint`

## Design

- Follow [DESIGN.md](../../DESIGN.md) and [PRODUCT.md](../../PRODUCT.md)
- Use semantic utilities: `.text-heading`, `.text-prose`, `.text-meta`, `.text-accent`, `.border-subtle` — not raw zinc/lime in components
- One `.signal-mark` per page hero; no box shadows; 44px touch targets + `.focus-ring`

## Commits

Only commit when the user asks. Do not commit `.impeccable/critique/`.
